=== Command line Facebook status update bot v1.0 ===

Readme date: Nov 2 2011
Contributors: lukapusic
Author: Luka Pusic <pusic93@gmail.com>
URI: http://360percents.com/posts/bash-script-to-update-facebook-status-linux-mac-os-x/

== Description ==
Facebook status update bot updates your Facebook status without any API's, just with PHP's curl extension.


== System requirements ==
* unix like OS (works also on Mac OS X;)
* curl

== Instructions ==
1. appy permissions: chmod +x ./fb.sh
2. open fb.sh and edit email and password fields
3. run it

== Changelog ==
*

== Known issues ==
* Facebook's new device checking causes this script to fail

